body:
Hi Guys,

Challenger Level (ended season diamond because of laziness but now 400+ pt challenger) player.

Hoping to get 100 likes so I can start to release some fun stuff, guides and other content. Express your interest with a like!

Also, Feel free to ask any questions on the page and I'll answer everything best I can :)
